Visteon solely supplies automotive components and systems to vehicle manufacturers for factory installation and does not sell products or replacement parts to individual consumers, dealers or distributors. Inquiries regarding part supply and repair should be directed to the vehicle manufacturer’s dealership network. Please consult the vehicle manufacturer’s website for a list of dealerships.
