Global Opportunities
The  career opportunities available at Visteon are as broad and diverse as our  global employees. We have employees in 18 countries who work together as  one team, sharing the same goals and vision. Working at Visteon, you’ll learn  what it’s like to work for an international corporation with employees in just  about every time zone. You may even have an opportunity to work on an overseas  assignment to further develop your career. 





To  learn more about career opportunities available, select from a country below:





Brazil
Bulgaria
China
France
Germany
India


Japan
Macedonia
Mexico
Portugal
Russia
Slovakia




South Korea
Thailand
Tunisia
United Kingdom
United States







Follow Visteon:













 
 
Notice to Employment Agencies and Professional Recruiters: Visteon will not accept unsolicited resumes from any source other than directly from a candidate. Any employment agency or professional recruiter (“Agency”) that submits an unsolicited resume to Visteon’s career site or directly to any employee, does so with the understanding that the resume will become the property of Visteon. Visteon will have the right to hire that candidate at its discretion without any fee owed to the Agency.
    Agencies that have fee agreements with Visteon and have been engaged on a specific search shall follow the submission process outlined by the Visteon recruiter with whom they are partnering with on the search.
    All inquiries by Agencies to become a provider of recruiting services must be directed to and approved by Visteon’s Director of Global Talent Acquisition.

 
